<cb:div>
<pb n="0119a" xml:id="I01.0047.0119a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0119a00" type="honorific"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><cb:docNumber>No. 47</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0119a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>朱永隆七十人等造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0119a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0119a0101">夫鏡日輝玄。<note n="0119001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">啔＝啓【史】</note><note n="0119001" resp="ihp" type="mod">啔【佛拓】，啓【史】</note><app n="0119001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">啓</lem><rdg wit="【原】">啔</rdg></app>妙識於淨海。澄波洰<note n="0119002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30319"/>＝壑【史】</note><note n="0119002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30319"/>【佛拓】，壑【史】</note><app n="0119002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">壑</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30319"/></rdg></app>。運境目於生源。是以八相同紛。闢重<note n="0119003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30285"/>＝關【史】</note><note n="0119003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30285"/>【佛拓】，關【史】</note><app n="0119003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">關</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30285"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0119a02" type="honorific"/>於幽夜。三輪<note n="0119004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">昞＝昺【史】</note><note n="0119004" resp="ihp" type="mod">昞【佛拓】，昺【史】</note><app n="0119004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">昺</lem><rdg wit="【原】">昞</rdg></app>轍。闡神機於正路。<note n="0119005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𠉕＝使【史】</note><note n="0119005" resp="ihp" type="mod">𠉕【佛拓】，使【史】</note><app n="0119005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">使</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𠉕</rdg></app>遊子歸衢。輕車<note n="0119006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨑷＝迅【史】</note><note n="0119006" resp="ihp" type="mod">𨑷【佛拓】，迅【史】</note><app n="0119006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">迅</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨑷</rdg></app>駕。炎宅止<note n="0119007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">燌＝焚【史】</note><note n="0119007" resp="ihp" type="mod">燌【佛拓】，焚【史】</note><app n="0119007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">焚</lem><rdg wit="【原】">燌</rdg></app>。冰池攸淥。
<lb ed="I" n="0119a03" type="honorific"/>故能振馨風於沖漠之野。擊玉磬於<note n="0119a0301" resp="CBETA" type="add">无【CB】，旡【原】【史】</note><app n="0119a0301"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>聲之<note n="0119008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30321"/>＝鄉【史】</note><note n="0119008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30321"/>【佛拓】，鄉【史】</note><app n="0119008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鄉</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30321"/></rdg></app>。遂大鵬奮霄。龍<note n="0119009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30322"/>＝翔【史】</note><note n="0119009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30322"/>【佛拓】，翔【史】</note><app n="0119009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">翔</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30322"/></rdg></app><note n="0119010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𥪰＝競【史】</note><note n="0119010" resp="ihp" type="mod">𥪰【佛拓】，競【史】</note><app n="0119010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">競</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𥪰</rdg></app>湊。六合<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">雲</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0119a04" type="honorific"/>翻。十方斯集。金言演暢。豪光九<note n="0119011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𤋜＝照【史】</note><note n="0119011" resp="ihp" type="mod">𤋜【佛拓】，照【史】</note><app n="0119011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">照</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𤋜</rdg></app>。法界融蕩。瓊<note n="0119012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30323"/>＝華【史】</note><note n="0119012" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30323"/>【佛拓】，華【史】</note><app n="0119012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">華</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30323"/></rdg></app>七瑩。乃塵沙涉靜浪之舟。□
<lb ed="I" n="0119a05" type="honorific"/>形蒙麾棹之緣。於是騰超彼<note n="0119013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30324"/>＝岸【史】</note><note n="0119013" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30324"/>【佛拓】，岸【史】</note><app n="0119013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">岸</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30324"/></rdg></app>。濟度<note n="0119a0501" resp="CBETA" type="add">无【CB】，旡【原】【史】</note><app n="0119a0501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>崖。必以朝露易<note n="0119014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30325"/>＝晞【史】</note><note n="0119014" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30325"/>【佛拓】，晞【史】</note><app n="0119014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">晞</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30325"/></rdg></app>。浮霜難固。提河早流。
<lb ed="I" n="0119a06" type="honorific"/>皓林促<note n="0119015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30326"/>＝變【史】</note><note n="0119015" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30326"/>【佛拓】，變【史】</note><app n="0119015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">變</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30326"/></rdg></app>。隱影靈遷。圓明息曜。三界悲動。四生<note n="0119016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30327"/>＝號【史】</note><note n="0119016" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30327"/>【佛拓】，號【史】</note><app n="0119016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">號</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30327"/></rdg></app>慕。賢徒泣血。能言瀝地。大
<lb ed="I" n="0119a07" type="honorific"/>聖垂慈。敷十二以流導。悲愍將來。布舍利以昌迹。故優填鐫姿。育王建塔。所在
<lb ed="I" n="0119a08" type="honorific"/>模容。流芳万國。自尒暨今。邁餘千載。寺有魏大法師故沙門都法恩。起妙因於
<lb ed="I" n="0119a09" type="honorific"/>初心。建淨業於<note n="0119a0901" resp="CBETA" type="add">无【CB】，旡【原】【史】</note><app n="0119a0901"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>始。故童年去或。高步<note n="0119017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𦃠＝緇【史】</note><note n="0119017" resp="ihp" type="mod">𦃠【佛拓】，緇【史】</note><app n="0119017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">緇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𦃠</rdg></app>門。逍遙法菀。矯志松蘭。縕思玄蹤。物
<lb ed="I" n="0119a10" type="honorific"/>我俱懷。遂捨衣鉢之餘。採石名山。訪巧求能。願雕真容。但<note n="0119a1001" resp="CBETA" type="add">无【CB】，旡【原】【史】</note><app n="0119a1001"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>常驚逝。峰烟激速。
<lb ed="I" n="0119a11" type="honorific"/>創福未周。奄從物化。門徒<note n="0119018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">㘁＝嗥【史】</note><note n="0119018" resp="ihp" type="mod">㘁【佛拓】，嗥【史】</note><app n="0119018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">嗥</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㘁</rdg></app>戀。精感<note n="0119019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB02793"/>＝彌【史】</note><note n="0119019" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB02793"/>【佛拓】，彌【史】</note><app n="0119019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB02793"/></rdg></app><note n="0119020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">䔍＝篤【史】</note><note n="0119020" resp="ihp" type="mod">䔍【佛拓】，篤【史】</note><app n="0119020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">篤</lem><rdg wit="【原】">䔍</rdg></app>。又弟子法度。戒行冰朗。智超空有。仰
<lb ed="I" n="0119a12" type="honorific"/>稟師則。磬志忠誠。更崇妍瑑。妙<note n="0119021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30329"/>＝鏤【史】</note><note n="0119021" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30329"/>【佛拓】，鏤【史】</note><app n="0119021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鏤</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30329"/></rdg></app>金顏。釋迦怡怡。若兜率之趣琦殿。<note n="0119022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𢏏＝彌【史】</note><note n="0119022" resp="ihp" type="mod">𢏏【佛拓】，彌【史】</note><app n="0119022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𢏏</rdg></app>勒昂昂。
<lb ed="I" n="0119a13" type="honorific"/>狀龍華之啓三會。多寶同坐。事等湧出。飛堪絙虛。<note n="0119023" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30330"/>＝旋【史】</note><note n="0119023" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30330"/>【佛拓】，旋【史】</note><app n="0119023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">旋</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30330"/></rdg></app>瓔<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">反</unclear>入。維摩權形。嘿言於
<lb ed="I" n="0119a14" type="honorific"/>方丈。文殊十辭。表問疾於平等。菩薩諸天。簫瑟芙麗。金剛密跡。獻目楊<note n="0119024" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">堦＝階【史】</note><note n="0119024" resp="ihp" type="mod">堦【佛拓】，階【史】</note><app n="0119024"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">階</lem><rdg wit="【原】">堦</rdg></app>。飾像
<lb ed="I" n="0119a15" type="honorific"/>雖訖。嵩塔未備。而度曉夕慇。<note n="0119025" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𧡃＝觀【史】</note><note n="0119025" resp="ihp" type="mod">𧡃【佛拓】，觀【史】</note><app n="0119025"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">觀</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𧡃</rdg></app>成神宇。不謂暴疾所鐘。潛魂深夜。致使營　圖
<lb ed="I" n="0119a16" type="honorific"/>中癈。為山止匱。復有此寺上坐僧惠。寺主法合。並湛潔內融。皎志方外。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">持</unclear>四<note n="0119026" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30332"/>＝攝【史】</note><note n="0119026" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30332"/>【佛拓】，攝【史】</note><app n="0119026"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">攝</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30332"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0119a17" type="honorific"/>於匈衿。騁七<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">臠</unclear>於神膺。洞博群經。智遊<note n="0119a1701" resp="CBETA" type="add">无【CB】，旡【原】【史】</note><app n="0119a1701"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app><note n="0119027" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">㝵＝礙【史】</note><note n="0119027" resp="ihp" type="mod">㝵【佛拓】，礙【史】</note><app n="0119027"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">礙</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㝵</rdg></app>。<note n="0119028" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30746"/>＝緇【史】</note><note n="0119028" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30746"/>【佛拓】，緇【史】</note><app n="0119028"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">緇</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30746"/></rdg></app>素同遵。歸依各流。又邑主朱永
<lb ed="I" n="0119a18" type="honorific"/>隆。唐豐七十人等。各槃根蘭冑。挺茂華芳。樤葩槐蕀。籍潤斯遠。發悟自天。契達
<lb ed="I" n="0119a19" type="honorific"/>幽旨。普相率厲。敦崇邑義。以其處也。碧地流泉。勢俠中都。金豪光泗。鬱澤新鮮。
<lb ed="I" n="0119a20" type="honorific"/>蓊林翠柏。璨然在目。布寶求園。謂莫斯過。遂採棟雲臺。代木方巖。班匠麗功。造
<lb ed="I" n="0119a21" type="honorific"/>天宮一<note n="0119029" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">塸＝區【史】</note><note n="0119029" resp="ihp" type="mod">塸【佛拓】，區【史】</note><app n="0119029"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">區</lem><rdg wit="【原】">塸</rdg></app>。巍巍赫<note n="0119030" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30333"/>＝奕【史】</note><note n="0119030" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30333"/>【佛拓】，奕【史】</note><app n="0119030"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">奕</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30333"/></rdg></app>。媚若祇桓。堂堂<app type="star" corresp="#0119004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">昺</lem><rdg wit="【原】">昞</rdg></app>煥。婉踰神塔。迷者一闞。則洗或於先源。
<lb ed="I" n="0119a22" type="honorific"/>慧者暫睹。則感悟於後際。可謂福潤含生。祚隆<app type="star" corresp="#0119022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𢏏</rdg></app><note n="0119031" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">刼＝劫【史】</note><note n="0119031" resp="ihp" type="mod">刼【佛拓】，劫【史】</note><app n="0119031"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">劫</lem><rdg wit="【原】">刼</rdg></app>。酬功報德。鐫石遐芳。
<lb ed="I" n="0119a23" type="honorific"/>其詞曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0119a24" type="honorific"/>皎皎淨性。洸洸境日。湛波<app type="star" corresp="#0119001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">啓</lem><rdg wit="【原】">啔</rdg></app>旭。騰源曜質。現託王宮。曠周遐悉。鸞翔□翥。法□
<lb ed="I" n="0119a25" type="honorific"/>斯一。　大音唱諭。名義弗違。淨光電掃。輕舟返飛。浮烟靜霧。赫日□□。致遷景
<lb ed="I" n="0119a26" type="honorific"/>覺。人天<note n="0119032" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𠕀＝罔【史】</note><note n="0119032" resp="ihp" type="mod">𠕀【佛拓】，罔【史】</note><app n="0119032"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">罔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𠕀</rdg></app>歸。　三千號慟。沖影潛空。愍彼長迷。敷此幽綜。爰有哲士。紹隆聖蹤。
<lb ed="I" n="0119a27" type="honorific"/>彫珉鐫像。以表靈容。　英信等悟。磬寶脩圖。福延<app type="star" corresp="#0119022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𢏏</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0119031"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">劫</lem><rdg wit="【原】">刼</rdg></app>。鏡水非<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">虛</unclear>。善潤　皇家。
<lb ed="I" n="0119a28" type="honorific"/>祚融唐虞。蠢尒同津。咸契凝如。
<lb ed="I" n="0119a29" type="honorific"/>　　　　　大魏武定三年歲次乙丑七月戊寅朔十五日壬辰樹</p>
